message.body: Cuz! What time should we come over and what should we bring tomorrow?! Looking forward to it!
Hey cuz!!! What time you guys want to come? Andrews appt got moved to the morning.
You guys can come whenever. It's going to be HOT tomorrow. Haha.
Cool! Is it cool if we come around 5:30-6? We can bring stuff for a salad!
Yeah that would actually be perfect! Timing is perfect too. I'll probably feed the boys and Iliana ahead of time so we can eat in peace.
Great!! What's yr address for the gps?
Perfect! Can't wait! Call me if you guys need anything on our way!
Also the house isn't 100%!
Girl. Please you have four kids in the house!
The kids destroy and conquer during the day. :-)
Hahaha!
I'm not worried about you! I got hunter to meet. Haha. So excited to finally meet him.
Me too! He's been having fun today I think.
Haha it's your dad's. As long as he likes bugs, dirty mouths and a mini junk yard you are good. Haha
You nailed it.
Ahhh I'm so excited! You guys have a great camping evening! Love you!
Love you too! See you tmw can't wait! Sleep tight.
Hey does hunter like ice cream? Or cake?
Yes he loves ice cream especially!
Ok.
We also have special philly donuts for you!
And I can't wait for donuts!
What's hunters favorite ice cream
He usually gets moose tracks or something with caramel in it.
Ok sounds good.
We should be there in 45 to an hour, wanted to show Hunter Leesburg. See you soon!
